com.guidewire.ab.external.entity

Interface ABContactContact

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ABLinkable, CommonContactContact, gw.pl.external.entity.Entity, gw.pl.external.entity.KeyableEntity, Validatable, Versionable
    Deprecated. 
    External entities are deprecated. Please use the new Java API instead.

    @Deprecated
public interface ABContactContact
extends ABLinkable, CommonContactContact, Validatable, Versionable, gw.pl.external.entity.Entity
    The purpose of this table is to avoid a self-referencing foreign key on abcontact, and to allow contacts to relate to one another in different ways.
